cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CC, cs.SY

The paper describes a cognitive model based on the human brain, with automatic and distributed pattern activity, which suggests that it is likely to fall under the category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). The paper also discusses knowledge-based and experience-based clustering techniques, which are commonly used in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper proposes a new entropy-style equation, which could be relevant to Computational Complexity (cs.CC) and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
